<L>__{interior hunsecker's penthouse night}
<A>__{the ringing of the telephone is heard in the big room an impressively furnished apartment which has a decor indicating that the owner thinks of himself in epic terms. camera moves to discover hunsecker in robe and pajamas, tapping at his typewriter. taking his leisurely time, he picks up the phone and eventually answers it.}
